First Department,

June, 1953.

(June 2, 1953.) Peter Schwabe, Respondent, v. Consolidated Edison Company of New York, Inc., Defendant, and Tully & Di Napoli, Inc., Appellant.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion. Present — ■ Dore, J. P., Callahan, Breitel and Bergan, JJ.; Callahan, J., dissents and votes to reverse.
